column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr   FROM Galaxy as p    JOIN zooMonochromeBias AS zmb ON p.objid = zmb.objid    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.clean=# AND zmb.nvote_mon >= # AND zmb.p_cs_mon > #      AND p.dered_g/p.err_g > # AND p.dered_r/p.err_r > # AND s.z BETWEEN # and #
